{"tid":1469571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"二副機長「通風報信」遭停職","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:31:49.000Z","uid":94809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5bcd6a3e22f141ba92ed12e06d91ae17a0de05","tid":1469571,"uid":94809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"周一網上曾流傳警方會於傍晚6時清場，部分示威者隨即離開機場，期間有人上傳一張相信是國泰航班駕駛艙顯示屏相片，顯示航班即將出發回港，帖文要求已離開的人立刻返回機場，被指向示威者「通風報信」。國泰航空證實，一名二副機長因涉及不當使用公司資訊及違反公司內部行為守則，已被停職。國泰發言人表示，公司已展開內部紀律程序，一如既往，對涉及運作和航空安全事宜，會採取零容忍態度。<br />\n<br />\n今日信報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/headline/article/2219466/國泰轉飛大阪+否認禁入中國領空\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline%2Farticle%2F2219466%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%BD%89%E9%A3%9B%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%2B%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%A6%81%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E7%A9%BA&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0W9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=525cd79d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/headline/article/2219466/國泰轉飛大阪+否認禁入中國領空</a>"},{"pid":"90dd1ea4d7a86e19ad0950c9591315854c7070f0","tid":1469571,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\